{"tid":1199904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野餐必備良身","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:23:47.000Z","uid":41389,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2cbfba85bdeb48b80bf4b238d2437fff23cb694","tid":1199904,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"一、火槍 <br />\n最好propane torch 又快又方便點火準備BBQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0070/9355/1161/products/2_282cc206-9bc2-44cb-9533-50112c2432a9_1080x.png?v=1526730657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0070%2F9355%2F1161%2Fproducts%2F2_282cc206-9bc2-44cb-9533-50112c2432a9_1080x.png%3Fv%3D1526730657&h=fc9a7d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二、保溫壺＋滾水<br />\n<br />\n去野餐有野狗搵食少不了 但大家千萬不要用熱水驅趕 用黎消毒番跌落地既野食好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c.ecimg.tw/items/DEBW4VA9009Z04E/000001_1560131582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc.ecimg.tw%2Fitems%2FDEBW4VA9009Z04E%2F000001_1560131582.jpg&h=e34c8052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三、酒精<br />\n去野餐開番幾瓶三蒸酒飲是常識吧 但記住千奇唔好點著火呀 後果不堪設想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.pearlriverbridge.com/US/1/48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.pearlriverbridge.com%2FUS%2F1%2F48.png&h=8869daf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四、油<br />\n帶定油去煮送是常識吧 但千奇唔好倒瀉落馬路 辛苦曬啲清潔呀姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gaitaobao4.alicdn.com/tfscom/i1/1626234032/O1CN012UanWj1fehQqfuKzH_!!1626234032.jpg_400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaitaobao4.alicdn.com%2Ftfscom%2Fi1%2F1626234032%2FO1CN012UanWj1fehQqfuKzH_%21%211626234032.jpg_400x400.jpg&h=5a09b737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五、糖<br />\n見到車油缸有糖要提醒千奇唔好開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4413c07bbd61a135414a99cf73487a292cf19c27","tid":1199904,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}